    "Body": " Email Marketing & CRM Specialist The Company: We are a decentralized ICO Venture Capital Fund investing in disruptive Blockchain/Crypto projects. We provide companies with $0.5M - $1.5M in venture capital financing, Blockchain incubation and global compliant ICO execution. In doing so we provide trust, confidence and recurring income to ICO crowd investors for their investments in scalable blockchain projects. The Role: As the Email Marketing & CRM Specialist you will be responsible for defining and executing on the email marketing activation/retention strategy, ensuring effective delivery of email communication, and lead all aspects of the CRM & Email funnel management to achieve targets. Job description: \u2022 Coordinate with marketing team to plan, design and launch effective email marketing campaigns. \u2022 Develop and execute email promotional plans and lead generation tactics. \u2022 Execution of email marketing activities: email campaign set up, email database segmentation, ensuring the right newsletters are sent to the right segments. \u2022 Develop and maintain an email segmentation and deployment calendar. \u2022 Understand customer behaviors and characteristics to optimize email marketing performance, by analyzing, mining, and reporting on customer data. \u2022 Design and run email marketing campaigns with A/B testing. \u2022 Proactively monitor email marketing KPIs (open rates, click-through rates, conversion rates, etc.) and continuously improve email marketing campaigns. \u2022 Manage the sales funnel and improve conversions at each stage: new lead >> active lead >> first time customer >> repeat customer >> VIP customer. \u2022 Regularly analyze data to develop actionable hypotheses and conclusions. \u2022 Create weekly and monthly reports for CRM activities, detailing your findings and then communicate those insights to senior management. Requirements: \u2022 3+ years online marketing experience, specifically email marketing & CRM involving lead generation, customer segmentation, activation and retention. \u2022 Excellent understanding of direct marketing best practices and analytics. \u2022 Ability to develop and implement retention marketing strategies and assess marketing performance \u2022 Strong analytical skills and ability to draw on analysis and formulate solutions. \u2022 Knowledge of evaluating marketing and commercial ROI, conversion funnel analysis and optimization. Knowledge of Google Analytics. \u2022 Experience with Mailchimp or similar enterprise Email Marketing System. \u2022 A healthy mix of analytical and creative skills, with a strong bias towards getting stuff done. Growth Hacker mindset! \u2022 High levels of accuracy and attention to detail are essential. \u2022 Must have the ability to work under pressure and work to deadlines. \u2022 Ability to work with minimal guidance and demonstrate self-starter qualities. \u2022 Excellent English communication (verbal and written). Why join CentrumCoin? \u2022 Be a part of the Crypto/Blockchain and ICO Revolution. \u2022 Work with highly intelligent and driven people who display a high degree of initiative, motivation and flexibility. \u2022 Work in an entrepreneurial setting that supports openness to innovative ideas. \u2022 Get exposure to various career opportunities within the organization. The position can be based either in Budapest or Moscow. Apply Now! Send your CV and Cover Letter by email to [email????????????protected] with the subject line \"Email Marketing Specialist\" and state why you're best suited for the job. We are looking to hire immediately. Learn more about CentrumCoin via our website: www.centrumcoin.com Skills Online marketing, direct marketing, CRM Compensation 2k-4k EUR ", 
